# UI Consistency Rules

- Use Quasar defaults first; no custom layout shells when `q-page` + `q-card` + `q-table` fit.
- Page wrapper: `q-page.bw-page` > `.bw-page__stack` > content.
- Page header: `AppPageHeader` from `components/ui/AppPageHeader.vue` with `action` slot.
- Section container: `q-card flat bordered`.
- List data: `q-table`; card grids: `.bw-entity-grid` with plain `q-card`.
- Colors: use `var(--bw-theme-*)` tokens from `web/src/css/app.scss`; never hardcode except domain table highlights.
- Primary button: max one `color="primary" unelevated` per page header.
- Secondary: `flat` or `outline`; danger: `color="negative"`.
- No default refresh buttons on app management pages.
- No FABs when header action is sufficient.
- Errors: `q-banner.bw-status-banner` with `bg-negative text-white` (or scope-appropriate).
- Empty lists: `.empty-state-block.floating-surface` or centered `.empty-state` column with muted text.
- Loading (page): `PageInitialLoader`; background requests: `GlobalAjaxBar`.
- In-table loading: `q-skeleton` rows only for high-density ops tables (Thrift pattern).
- Toasts/dialogs: `showSuccessNotification`, `showErrorNotification`, `showWarningNotification`, `requestConfirmation` from `utils/appFeedback.ts` only.
- Forms: match page `outlined`/`filled` style; use `.soft-input` for themed fields.
- Spacing: `.bw-page` padding, `.bw-page__stack` gap `1.25rem`, `.bw-entity-grid` gap `1rem`.
- Border radius: buttons `8px`, surfaces `14px` (`.floating-surface`), hero `16px` (`.hero-surface`).
- `q-page` max-width `1200px`; treasury/report pages need `min-width: 0` on flex/grid parents.
- Treasury pages: `TreasuryPageShell` > `TreasuryStatGrid` > `TreasuryTableWrap` > `q-table` with explicit `min-width`.
- Dense ops detail: follow `docs/PAGE_HEADER.md` DETAIL + status workflow strip (not chip menus); rates/secondary editors collapsed by default; table full width.
- Page headers (list/detail): prefer `docs/PAGE_HEADER.md` over `AppPageHeader` for new app management pages.
- High-density table column pastels: weight `#e8d7f7`, price `#daf3e4`, cost `#ffe8d1`, qty `#d0e6ff`.
- No `backdrop-filter` on static headers/cards/toolbars.
- New shared component only if used on 2+ pages; place in `web/src/components/ui/`.
- Reference implementations: `TenantPage.vue`, `AdminTenantPage.vue`, `ModulesPage.vue`.
